title: #92Noon! Charch in for PA! Oake in Studio/Greenway/Trades That Broke Your Heart
description: Paul Charchian is in for PA, and is joined by Brian Oake   in studio and it's nothing but music, music, music and a little reminiscing. Chad Greenway calls in to discuss the Washington Redskins changing their name. And the Minnesota trade that broke your heart, taking your calls and hearing what you have to say.
